body:
### Summary of the new feature / enhancement

The lack of milliseconds as a parameter to New-Timespan seems like a needless omission from the parameter set.

Please could we add it, I assume it is an easy one

### Proposed technical implementation details (optional)

Add a new parameter 

        /// <summary>
        /// Allows the user to override the millisecond.
        /// </summary>
        [Parameter(ParameterSetName = "Time")]
        public int Milliseconds { get; set; }

pass it to 

result = new TimeSpan(Days, Hours, Minutes, Seconds, Milliseconds);
